description: Try our easy to follow Cheesy Hot Dogs recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Cheesy Hot Dogs Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 8 extra-soft jumbo hot dog rolls, split
750ml Wine option: Cat Amongst the Pigeons Shiraz
750ml Wine option: South Island Marlborough Sauvignon Blanc

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 180Â°C. Place the hot dog rolls on an ovenproof tray and heat for 10 minutes or until heated through.
Meanwhile, cook frankfurts in boiling water for 5 minutes or until heated through.
Place hot dog rolls on a serving tray and fill each with a frankfurt and pickles. Drizzle with tomato sauce and mustard. Sprinkle over cheese and top with rocket. Serve with potato crisps.
